==New to OpenTTD Wiki? == 
* If you are new to wikis, you may want to read the [[en/Tutorial|Tutorial]].
* Please ensure your contributions fall in line with editing [[en/Main/Manual of Style|Manual of Style]] guidelines.
* Dont forget you can always test/practice in the [[en/Main/Sandbox|Sandbox]] and request assistance/discuss at the Talk page.


==How to help out==
* If you want to help but you're not sure where to start, try [[:Category:en/Articles to be expanded|improving]] and [[:Category:en/Articles to be updated|updating]] the various articles by adding content. 
* You can also create new articles, make sure to check the list of [[en/Special/Wantedpages|wanted pages]] for frequently linked-to articles that don't exist yet.
* To follow the changes to this wiki, and to look out for new users and edits use [[en/Special/RecentChanges|recent changes]].
* You can find a list of useful templates on [[:Category:en/Templates]], some of which are documented [[en/Main/Templates|here]].
* If you need help editing, you could start with [[en/Tutorial|Tutorial]] and [[en/Trash/Editing help|Editing help]] page.


